dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows cities, main routes, various Y.M.C.A. facilities and services.
Two radial lines, one solid, one dotted, centered on Coblenz.
G-2-C seal under title represents the Topographical, Map Supply, and Sound and Flash Ranging Division of American Expeditionary Forces during World War 1.
